---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "The Afterlife Series | The Teachings"
description: "Exploring how different traditions understand death, rebirth, and the soul’s journey."
tier: free
---

{% block head %}
  {% set socialImage = "/TGK-assets/images/share/the-teachings/afterlife-index.jpg" %}
  {% include "partials/head-meta.njk" %}

  {# JSON-LD: set vars first, then include #}
  {% set items = collections.content | bySeries("the-afterlife") | sortByEpisode %}
  {% set headline = "The Afterlife — Episodes" %}
  {% set base = "" %}
  {% include "partials/jsonld-collection.njk" %}
{% endblock %}

<main class="main-content">
  <section class="page-title-block">
    <p class="page-title">Death is not the end. It is the map home. This series explores the afterlife across hidden traditions.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="portal-grid">
    {% for ep in collections.content | bySeries("the-afterlife") | sortByEpisode %}
      <a href="{{ ep.url }}" class="gnostic-card">
        <div class="gnostic-card-inner">
          <div class="gnostic-card-glyph">☉</div>
          <h2 class="gnostic-card-title">{{ ep.data.title }}</h2>
          {% if ep.data.description %}
            <div class="gnostic-card-tagline">{{ ep.data.description }}</div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </section>

  <div class="gnostic-divider">
    <span class="divider-symbol pillar-glyph spin glow" aria-hidden="true">☉</span>
  </div>
</main>
